A Hospitality Experience Like No Other","consider-as-h1[]":["Yes"],"snippet-description":"

When we acquired the Lewis Center property in the 1950s, it was situated in a remote, underdeveloped region.

Fast forward to today, and the property is a vibrant hub of progress and development. The site has become an anchor point in a thriving community — growing better and more dynamic each year.

What began as a radio station in the 40’s evolved into Green Meadows Inn during the 60’s, which later transformed into a training center for Nationwide Insurance agents in the 70’s, and ultimately expanded into a full-scale conference and hotel by the early 00’s.

","snippet-description-more":"

As the region continues to grow, we’re committed to providing a premier destination for families, businesses, and communities to come together to connect, celebrate, build partnerships, and make memories that will last a lifetime.

As is typical in the life cycle of all great hotels and event facilities, it was time for a comprehensive renovation and rebranding. We took the opportunity to reimagine our property for the authentic Ohioan.

We are excited to renovate this historic property, preserving its rich character while introducing modern features that enhance both its beauty and functionality. By maintaining its integrity and authenticity, we are building upon an already vibrant property to create a space that is both timeless and forward-thinking.

The Ohioan is an anchor in our great state — the elevated event center offers a reputation of rich history and stately appeal that is reflective of the property itself.

Our campus-like setting with graceful Georgian architecture, quaint cobblestone footpaths, and endless natural beauty provides a stunning outdoor wedding space in Columbus for ceremonies, receptions and photography. Our professional wedding staff can help to transform any of our lovely outdoor spaces into an unforgettable scene.

  • Tranquil poolside patio overlooking a serene pond—perfect for relaxed gatherings or sunset cocktails 
  • Brick-paved terrace framed by stunning arched, floor-to-ceiling windows that blend indoor elegance with outdoor charm 
  • Lush, manicured lawns shaded by mature trees and accented with vibrant seasonal landscaping 
  • Elegant white pergola adorned with cascading wisteria vines, creating a romantic and picturesque setting

Your wedding day deserves to be as unique as your love story. Our wedding packages at The Ohioan Hotel & Event Center are designed to offer you flexibility, luxury, and an unforgettable experience. With three beautifully designed reception spaces and customizable packages, you can bring your vision to life. 

","snippet-description-more":"

Choose from our Silver, Gold, and Platinum packages, each carefully crafted to provide a seamless and stress-free event experience. From full-service dinners and rehearsal spaces to a dedicated venue coordinator, we take care of all the details so you can focus on celebrating your special day.

The Ohioan Hotel & Event Center offers a variety of indoor and outdoor spaces for groups of every size, and our professional event planners will handle every detail so you can enjoy every minute. After a full day of learning, collaborating, and connecting, attendees will appreciate the comfort and convenience of our onsite hotel—featuring 193 upscale guest rooms and suites just steps from the event spaces

No matter the occasion, The Ohioan is an experience your guests will never forget. When we say, \"All we do is everything\", we mean it! We've hosted a Pig Roast, Mardi Gras parties, A Night in Paris, Fall Harvest Gala, OSU Tailgates and countless other themed events.

At The Ohioan Hotel & Event Center, we offer thoughtfully curated meeting packages designed to maximize impact and minimize stress. Upscale comfort, thoughtfully designed, The Ohioan Hotel & Event Center features 193 beautifully appointed guest rooms and suites that blend residential-style comfort with the elevated experience of an upscale boutique stay. Each room is curated with the modern traveler in mind—whether you're here for a conference, retreat, social event, or extended business stay. 


Enjoy complimentary high-speed wireless internet, VOIP telephones with speakerphone and voicemail, pillow-top mattresses, a full-length mirror, in-room refrigerators, and a premium in-room coffee experience, with upscale European bath amenities by TempleSpa. In addition, all rooms have our state-of-the-art audio-visual technology, which allows you to hook up your devices to our flat panel TVs. With a variety of room and suite options available, you can choose accommodations tailored to your preferences—ensuring a restful stay just steps from your meeting or event.

Our IACC certified conference center features 35 meeting and breakout rooms, perfectly customizable for any kind of professional event. Choose from one of our inclusive meeting packages and receive special meeting room amenities like an on-site technology support specialist and state-of-the-art, integrated technology.

Our beautiful property is ideal for a romantic wedding. Our hotel has hosted hundreds of elegant weddings, and our on-site professional event team works with each couple to create the wedding of their dreams. 

View our hotel gallery to learn more about the Nationwide Hotel and Conference Center, and book your stay with us today!

Check-In / Check-Out   

Check-In Time: Starting at 3:00 pm

Check-Out Time: 12:00 pm

Minimum Age to Register: 21

Early Departure Fee

Early departure policy may vary depending on your reservation details. Please refer to your reservation confirmation to verify your early departure policy.

Late Check-Out Fee

Late check-out until 1:00 PM, based on availability. Late check-out after 1:00 PM will be subjected to a fee.

Cancellations   

Cancellation policies may vary depending on the rate or dates of your reservation. Please refer to your reservation confirmation to verify your cancellation policy. If you need further assistance, call the hotel at 614-880-4300.

Smoking

The Ohioan Hotel & Event Center is a smoke and tobacco-free facility. Smoking is permitted in designated areas. All Guest Rooms including balconies, are non-smoking.

In compliance with Ohio state law, smoking is prohibited in all guest rooms (including the room balconies) and buildings throughout the Ohioan Hotel & Event Center campus. There are two designated smoking areas: just south of the outdoor pool and on the far-north side of the Virginia building. Vapes and e-cigarettes are also prohibited in the rooms. Our Venue. Exceptional Results","consider-as-h1[]":["Yes"],"snippet-description":"

At The Ohioan Hotel & Event Center, our highest priority is delivering an exceptional meeting experience—every guest, every industry, every time. Whether you're hosting a strategic planning session, leadership retreat, training seminar, or team-building event, our Columbus venue is designed to support productivity and innovation. 
 

With 35 flexible conference and breakout rooms, our meeting spaces feature ergonomic furnishings, non-glare tabletops, tackable and writable wall surfaces, adjustable lighting, and individual climate controls—ensuring comfort and focus throughout the day.

","snippet-description-more":"

A dedicated on-site audiovisual expert is available to support everything from multimedia presentations to hands-on computer workshops, while our meeting planners and concierges provide seamless support from start to finish. 

Let us help you create a meeting experience that inspires collaboration, drives results, and leaves a lasting impression.

Stepping onto the secluded and park-like grounds of the Ohioan can feel like you’re worlds away from the hustle and bustle of a city, yet our Columbus hotel is close to a number of exciting attractions! As Ohio’s capital city, there are always tons of things to do and our hotel and conference center provides guests with a luxurious stay close to the action.

With our hotel’s prime location near the John Glenn Columbus Airport, guests from all over visit The Ohioan Hotel & Event Center to enjoy an elegant stay near Columbus.

Guests of The Ohioan Hotel & Event Center can indulge in a delicious 5-star breakfast without ever leaving the property! Each morning, wake up and head down to The Ohio Dining Room, our world-class on-site restaurant. Open for breakfast, it serves classic American cuisine in a beautiful setting overlooking the hotel’s sprawling grounds. Guests who book our Bed and Breakfast Package enjoy this decadent buffet as part of their overnight stay experience.

After a day of exploring, unwind at our inviting pub, featuring a variety of craft beers, cocktails, and flavorful pub fare—perfect for relaxing evenings or casual gatherings. Whether starting your day or ending your night, our dining options offer something exceptional at The Ohioan.
